| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0944 — Recovery Inhibition (blacksuit)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 5fad790a-d28e-544b-8b59-18780e0c3bfe"
